OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fsunny periods giving way to clear
OL,7,Fspells for a time. Colder than the
OL,8,Fprevious night, with a widespread
OL,9,Frural frost developing. Clouding over
OL,10,Ffrom northwest later in the night,
OL,11,Fwith temperatures rallying,
OL,12,Fculminating in a little rain in places.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FCloudy with a little rain in
OL,15,Fplaces initially. Becoming bright and
OL,16,Fbreezy into the afternoon, with sunny
OL,17,Fspells and the odd sharp shower,
OL,18,Fperhaps thundery. Near-normal
OL,19,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
